\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Sol Plaatjie University \'28SPU\'29 is a public higher education institution whose programmes have been accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of a Postgraduate Diploma in Language Education programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery from the Chapel Street\'2C Kimberley\'2C Kimberly Campus. \line \line The Institution is accredited to offer the following programmes in the field of Education in the contact mode of delivery\'3A\line - Bachelor of Education in Senior Phase and Further Education and Training Teaching\line - Bachelor of Education in Intermediate Phase Teaching\line - Bachelor of Education Honours in Curriculum Studies\line - Postgraduate Diploma in Language Education\cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
